                            <comment id="13895948" author="erickerickson" created="Sun, 9 Feb 2014 18:02:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;bq: Is there any chance, this will be merged to branch lucene_solr_4_3 / lucene_solr_4_4&lt;/p&gt;

